data.description: NO FLOOD INSURANCE REQUIRED!  Located on a corner lot in Lakeside Subdivision in Morgan City, this large home is well-kept and move-in ready. Home boasts 3 spacious bedrooms and 2.5 baths. If you like to entertain, you'll love the  den/entertainment area. The kitchen is open to a dining area and offers tons of storage and counter space. The utility room goes with the theme of the rest of the home in that it is spacious and roomy and could double as a craft room.  The backyard houses a large shed/workshop and a 15KW Honeywell whole home gas generator. The roof and HVAC system is 2-1/2 years old.  Home is ready to show anytime!  Current owners do have an FHA loan at a low interest rate that is assumable with buyer meeting approved credit and other conditions.
